And the Special One believes the ex-England star should stay in the Premier League and hinted his rivals should have done more to keep him.

When asked if he would make a cheeky bid to sign him, Mourinho told 5 Live: 'Or perhaps to take him on loan? 

'I'm not happy he leaves, I would love the Premier League to keep hold of the best players and I think he has more than those qualities to play in the Premier League.' 

